on\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 31, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104oco1665702562747.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oco1665702562747.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/oco1665702562747.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"oco1665702562747\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Collection Script Container\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Code container of an entity that is used for operations that handle the collection of entity occurrences (as opposed to individual occurrences).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"oco1665702562747__section_w2866ab1b5b3_w2867ab1b5_w2868ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d358743e51\"> Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115910e1_d115911e1_d115912e1\">The Collection Script code container can\n            contain:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44219e1_d44220e1_d44221e1\">Constant declarations with container scope </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44222e1_d44223e1_d44224e1\">System triggers </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44225e1_d44226e1_d44227e1\">Interactive triggers </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44228e1_d44229e1_d44230e1\">Operations </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Entries</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44231e1_d44232e1_d44233e1\">Functions </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115916e1_d115917e1_d115918e1\">Before you can activate operations in the\n            Collection Script container, you must first do the following:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44234e1_d44235e1_d44236e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115919e1_d115920e1_d115921e1\">Ensure that there is a \n                  <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fku1665702562837.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fku1665702562837.html\" title=\"Name of the signature that is automatically generated by Uniface for all collection operations within the current entity. If you do not specify a value, the default name is EntityNameCOLL, which you can accept or change.\">Collection Interface Name</a> for\n                  the modeled entity.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44237e1_d44238e1_d44239e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115922e1_d115923e1_d115924e1\">Enter ProcScript for your entity operations\n                  in the Collection Script container of the modeled entity.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44240e1_d44241e1_d44242e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115925e1_d115926e1_d115927e1\">Compile the entity operation signatures for\n                  the entity. You can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ceo</span> command line switch.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"oco1665702562747__li_d44243e1_d44244e1_d44245e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"oco1665702562747__p_d115928e1_d115929e1_d115930e1\">To call an operation in this container,\n                  obtain a collection handle using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$collhandle</span>, then use this\n                  handle to invoke the desired operation.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vrb1707739762002.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Operations</a><p>Operations are ProcScript modules that are analogous to methods in other programming languages; they perform specific actions and can be activated by other ProcScript modules, and even by non-Uniface components.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ugp1665702562025.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Occurrence Script Container</a><p>Code container for defining occurrence-level operations and triggers.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qlo1665702562573.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Public and Partner Operations</a><p>Operations can be modified using the public or partner modifier. Public operations can be invoked from other components. Partner operations can only be invoked from the component in which they are defined.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwf1665702562929.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$collhandle</a><p>Returns the handle of the specified entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enc1665702653522.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/ceo</a><p>Compile entity collection operations and occurrence operations.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614955\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Collection Script Container Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 31, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Collection Script Container Code container of an entity that is used for operations that handle the collection of entity occurrences (as opposed to individual occurrences). Description The Collection Script code container can contain: Constant declarations with container scope System triggers Interactive triggers Operations Entries Functions Before you can activate operations in the Collection Script container, you must first do the following: Ensure that there is a Collection Interface Name for the modeled entity. Enter ProcScript for your entity operations in the Collection Script container of the modeled entity. Compile the entity operation signatures for the entity. You can use the /ceo command line switch. To call an operation in this container, obtain a collection handle using $collhandle , then use this handle to invoke the desired operation. Related Links Operations Operations are ProcScript modules that are analogous to methods in other programming languages; they perform specific actions and can be activated by other ProcScript modules, and even by non-Uniface components. Occurrence Script Container Code container for defining occurrence-level operations and triggers. Public and Partner Operations Operations can be modified using the public or partner modifier. Public operations can be invoked from other components. Partner operations can only be invoked from the component in which they are defined. $collhandle Returns the handle of the specified entity. /ceo Compile entity collection operations and occurrence operations. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}